      <title>大众汽车表示，巴西可持续发展规则不应让汽车变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</link>
