      <title>摩根士丹利因市政证券违规被美国监管机构罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-is-fined-by-us-regulator-municipal-securities-violations-2024-02-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，美国监管机构对摩根士丹利处以 160 万美元的罚款，原因是摩根士丹利未能及时取消或关闭 239 笔失败的交易商间市政证券交易，并迅速采取措施获得对数月到期的数百只市政证券的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-is-fined-by-us-regulator-municipal-securities-violations-2024-02-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 16:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
